---User Guide---
This is an app created to show appreciation & support to the actor Johnny Depp.
When you open the app, you will be created with: 

The Home screen
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* A Title
* A Menu to navigate to 3 other pages
* A flashlight plugin
* 2 Gifs
* A "Favourite Movie" Button (that brings you to a page where you can pick your favourite Johnny Depp movie from a list)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Rum gone?
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* On this page is an embedded youtube fanmade video
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Jd's Song
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* On this page is another embedded fanmade video-
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Movies
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* On this page A list of all the movies Johnny has ever starred in can be found
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Flashlight
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* The addition of a flashlight & a button to toggle it on and off was implemented
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Favourite Movie
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* This button was created, to send you to a page where you can choose your favourite Johhny Depp movie from the list provided
